[
    {
        "source_sentence": "3父子合集經卷第十八",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝散大夫",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "試鴻臚卿宣梵大師賜紫",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b15_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "沙門臣日稱等奉　詔譯六界差別品第二十六之三佛言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬若有人於睡夢中與諸寶媛共相執持，是人覺已，憶念夢中所受妙觸，為實爾不？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b20_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b20_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b20_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人所夢執以為實，是智者不？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b21_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b21_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢中畢竟無有寶媛，況復有彼美妙觸耶？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b22_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人徒自疲勞，都無所得。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b23_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b23_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b24_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚癡異生寡聞無智，於可意觸而生愛樂，心生染著造如是業，身業三種、語業四種、意業三種，造作彼業，剎那遷謝。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b26_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是業滅已，不依東方南西北方四維上下中間而住，至命終時，見先所作，心想中現，如彼睡覺憶夢中事，最後識滅自業現前。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969b29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識為其主，業為攀緣，二種相因，初識生起，作業受報，皆不失壞。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或趣地獄，或墮傍生、琰摩羅界及阿脩羅，若人若天，同分種類相續不絕。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c03_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "最後識滅名為死蘊，最初識起名為生蘊。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c04_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c04_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼識起時，無所從來，滅無所至；",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其緣生時，無所從來，滅無所至；",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c06_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼業生時，無所從來，滅無所至。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c07_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有少法從於此世得至他世。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c07_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自性空故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是了知初識初識空，自業自業空，身識身識空，若滅滅空，若生生空，輪迴輪迴空，涅槃涅槃皆自性空，無有作者亦無受者，但隨世俗之所顯示，非第一義作是說也。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知諸根如幻境界如夢，一切諸法皆悉空寂，此名空解脫門；",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "空無空相，名無相解脫門；",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無相者則無希求，名無願解脫門。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c14_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若能了此三解脫門，與空共行菩提先道，廣大如法性，究竟如虛空；",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於此譬喻。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當如是知。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有人於睡夢中，持熱銅鍱以為衣服而自纏身。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c19_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人覺已，憶念夢中熾然銅鍱觸身苦惱，為實爾不？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c20_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c20_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c20_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c21_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人所夢執為真實，是智者不？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c21_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢中畢竟無熱銅鍱，況復觸身受苦惱耶？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人徒自疲勞都無有實。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0969c24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
