        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b08_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自性空故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b08_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是了知初識初識空，自業自業空，身識身識空，若滅滅空，若生生空，輪迴輪迴空，涅槃涅槃皆自性空。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b10_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "了知業報自性非有，無有作者亦無受者，但唯名相分別顯示。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b12_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知諸根如幻境界如夢，一切諸法皆悉空寂，此名空解脫門；",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b13_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "空無空相，名無相解脫門；",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b14_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無相者，則無希求，名無願解脫門。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若能了此三解脫門，與空共行，菩提先道，廣大如法界，究竟如虛空。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於此譬喻，當如是知。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b17_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如人夢中見彼幻師幻作五欲種種欲樂，自見其身為彼圍遶，受諸快樂。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人覺已，憶念夢中所作事業，為實爾不？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b20_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b20_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b20_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b20_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼於夢境執以為實，是智者不？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b21_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b21_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b21_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢中畢竟無彼幻師，況復變現五欲等事。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b22_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人徒自疲勞，都無有實。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0970b23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
