    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "各受其報，同類心品相續隨轉，最後識滅名為死蘊，最初識起名為生蘊。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b04_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身識生時，無所從來，滅無所至；",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼緣生時，無所從來，滅無所至；",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼業生時，無所從來，滅無所至。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有少法從於此世得至他世。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b07_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自性空故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是了知初識初識空，自業自業空，身識身識空，若滅滅空，若生生空，輪迴輪迴空，涅槃涅槃皆自性空，無有作者亦無受者，若業若報，皆不可得，但唯名相分別顯示。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b12_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸根如幻境界如夢，一切諸法自性空寂，此名空解脫門；",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "空無空相，名無相解脫門；",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無相者，則無希求，名無願解脫門。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b14_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若能了知三解脫門，與空共行，菩提先道，廣大如法界，究竟如虛空。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於此譬喻，當如是知。",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」父子合集經卷第十八",
        "from": "T11n0320_018:0971b18_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]